R \cap S
\langle x,x\rangle \in R \cap S
\langle x,y\rangle \in R \cap S
\langle y,x\rangle \in R \cap S
\langle x,y\rangle, \langle y,z\rangle \in R \cap S
\langle x,z\rangle \in R \cap S
P=R \cap S
(x,y) \in P
\implies (x,y) \in R \cap S 
\implies (x,y) \in R \wedge (x,y) \in S 
\implies ((y,x) \notin R \wedge (y,x) \notin S) \Rightarrow(x \ne y) 
\implies (y,x) \notin R \cap S 
\implies (y,x) \notin P 
